sentences.sentence: It is argued, stripping cartons of their branding will trigger no mass movement to quit.
sentences.translation: 有人认为，剥离纸盒上的品牌标识不会让大多数人戒烟。

sentences.sentence: There were cartons of cigarettes everywhere.
Cartons of Chinese food were arrayed on a large oak table.
sentences.translation: 成盒成盒的中国食物被摆放在一个大橡木桌上。
